			<div class="post-8461 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-bitcoin-2 tag-bitcoin tag-cyprus-bail-in tag-goldmoney tag-james-turk tag-michael-pento tag-moip tag-money-over-internet-protocol tag-murray-rothbard post_box top" id="post-8461">
